  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Those who will be in class one to six by the time of study

          -  Aged 5-18 years and found infected with either SCH, any STH or LF for treatment groups
             1,2 or 3 or infected with both SCH and LF for treatment group 4 and infected with all
             the three for treatment group 5

          -  Who are willing and consent and whose parents will consent, will be included in the
             study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Those with acute and chronic diseases other than the targeted infections and those
             with a history of any serious adverse drug reactions will not be included in the
             study.

